		</tr>
		<tr>
			<td>30 days before Election Day by mail</td>
		</tr>
	</tbody>
</table>


<p>*<span><span><span>In-person late registration at your county office or county-designated location ends at noon the day prior to the election. You can register and vote at your county office or county-designated location on Election Day.</span></span></span></p>

<p>*In Montana,&nbsp;you can still register and vote in the election by <a href="https://votemt.gov/frequently-asked-questions/" rel="noopener" target="_blank">late registration</a> at your county election office or designated location until noon the day prior to the election.</p>

<p><em>Updated on November 12, 2024.</em></p>

